title: American Horror Story Season 8 Theme Radioactive??
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I hate having to wait until Fall, but I love your videos leading up to the season!!!

Personally, I hope, that it's not a post apocalyptic type story. Even if there are mutants, I much prefer stories dealing with the supernatural. I liked Cult and thought Evan Peters' performance, especially in so many roles, was incredible. But, I missed the supernatural twist (aside from Twisty himself) in that season. Get better soon, Mary! ❤
Thank you Mother Supreme! I'm glad to see you back! Great news! Get well soon!!!
I'm hoping for a postapocalyptic story line! I really am
Mary! You have great ideas! I hope your predictions come true!!! ❤️
description:
American Horror Story Season 8 Theme Radioactive??

Twentieth Century Fox filed for a standard character mark for American Horror Story Radioactive and you know Mother Supreme had to investigate. Special thanks to AHS Leaks on Twitter for breaking the news and Zombiedude245 and Ezra for tagging me. What do you think about the wordmark AHS filed for? Do you think it’s the theme? Let me know in the comments.
